OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774144984
OL,3,CIran's long-range missiles can reach
OL,4,CEuropean cities, Israel warns
OL,6,FIran has developed long-range missiles
OL,7,Fcapable of reaching major European
OL,8,Fcities, Israel has warned.
OL,10,FIran targeted Diego Garcia in the
OL,11,FChagos Islands before the Government
OL,12,Fgave the US permission to strike
OL,13,Fmissile sites targeting the Strait of
OL,14,FHormuz on Friday, but it is not clear
OL,15,Fexactly when the two intermediate-
OL,16,Frange ballistic missiles were fired.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
