PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774144984
OL,3,CIran's long-range missiles can reach
OL,4,CEuropean cities, Israel warns
OL,6,FThe Israeli Defence Forces (IDF) said
OL,7,Fit was the first time Tehran had
OL,8,Flaunched a long-range missile since
OL,9,Fthe start of the war, and showed it is
OL,10,Fnow capable of reaching cities like
OL,11,FLondon, Paris or Berlin.
OL,13,F"We have been saying it: The Iranian
OL,14,Fterrorist regime poses a global
OL,15,Fthreat," the IDF said in a statement.
OL,17,FThe Israeli military claimed the
OL,18,Fmissiles could reach a distance of
OL,19,Faround 4,000km, posing a danger to
OL,20,Fdozens of countries in Europe, Asia
OL,21,Fand Africa.
