OL,3,CIran's long-range missiles can reach
OL,4,CEuropean cities, Israel warns
OL,6,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,7,Fcondemned Iran's missile strikes on
OL,8,Fthe joint US-UK base on Saturday while
OL,9,Fstressing that the UK will not be
OL,10,Fdrawn into a wider conflict.
OL,12,FShe said ministers support defensive
OL,13,Faction only and want to see a swift
OL,14,Fresolution to the war.
OL,16,FOne of the missiles was shot down by a
OL,17,FUS warship while the other failed in
OL,18,Fflight, the Wall Street Journal
OL,19,Freported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
