OL,3,CIran's long-range missiles can reach
OL,4,CEuropean cities, Israel warns
OL,6,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,7,Furged the Prime Minister to "come
OL,8,Fclean" about the details of the latest
OL,9,Fattack on British troops and explain
OL,10,Fwhy the public was not informed.
OL,12,F"Keir Starmer has dithered and delayed
OL,13,Fon the Iran conflict from the outset,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
OL,16,F"Now we find out, from the media and
OL,17,Fnot the Prime Minister, that the
OL,18,FBritish base on Diego Garcia has been
OL,19,Fthe target of Iranian missile attacks.
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@FO]tD@AOUuD@fO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
