CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774144984
OL,3,CIran's long-range missiles can reach
OL,4,CEuropean cities, Israel warns
OL,6,F"The Prime Minister needs to
OL,7,Fimmediately come clean about the
OL,8,Fdetails of this latest attack on
OL,9,FBritish troops and explain why the
OL,10,Fpublic weren't informed sooner."
OL,12,FThe Ministry of Defence (MoD) has so
OL,13,Ffar declined to comment on when the
OL,14,Fattack was launched.
OL,16,FSir Keir spoke to Cypriot president
OL,17,FNikos Christodoulides on Saturday
OL,18,Fmorning, reiterating that RAF Akrotiri
OL,19,Fwill not be used by the US to target
OL,20,FIranian missile sites.
