OL,3,CIran's long-range missiles can reach
OL,4,CEuropean cities, Israel warns
OL,6,FHe also spoke to the Crown Prince of
OL,7,FBahrain, Salman bin Hamad Al Khalifa,
OL,8,Fto discuss the war.
OL,10,FDiego Garcia is around 3,800km (2,360
OL,11,Fmiles) away from Iran and home to an
OL,12,Fairbase capable of accommodating long-
OL,13,Frange US bombers.
OL,15,FThe UK has agreed to cede sovereignty
OL,16,Fof the islands to Mauritius and lease
OL,17,Fback the base.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
