CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1774144984
OL,3,CIran's long-range missiles can reach
OL,4,CEuropean cities, Israel warns
OL,6,FDiego Garcia is strategically valuable
OL,7,Fto the US and has been used as a
OL,8,Flaunchpad for operations in the Middle
OL,9,FEast for years.
OL,11,FIt has a large airfield, major fuel
OL,12,Fstorage facilities, radar
OL,13,Finstallations and a deep-water port
OL,14,Fand is home to about 2,500 mostly
OL,15,FAmerican personnel.
OL,17,FIran has escalated attacks on its Gulf
OL,18,Fneighbours in recent days while
OL,19,Fkeeping a stranglehold on shipping in
OL,20,Fthe Strait of Hormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
